<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.1">
<l>kiḷarntuntu ventuyar vantaṭum pōtañci neñcameṉpāyt</l>
<l>taḷarntiṅ kiruttaṟ ṟavirtikaṇ ṭāytaḷa rātuvanti</l>
<l>vaḷarntuntu kaṅkaiyum vāṉat tiṭaivaḷar kōṭṭuveḷḷai</l>
<l>yiḷantiṅ kaḷumeruk kummiruk kuñceṉṉi yīcaṉukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You named heart, being afraid at the time rising swelling hot misery comes [and] fells [you],</l>
<l>refrain from sitting here feebly, see: without slackening pay homage</l>
<l>to the lord with a head, on which sit the growing rising Gaṅgā,</l>
<l>the young moon white in a crescent in the sky and the Yarcum.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
